{"tid":1358192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［出師有名］向警鄉黑發出最後通牒 否則727將光復元朗","createTime":"2019-07-24T01:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:18:15.000Z","uid":132287,"like":22,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e4bc274ff96f4a52dccc46d76a6f665519add8f3","tid":1358192,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:18:29.000Z","msg":"大家之前咁鍾意家死線 點解今次唔定<br />\n<br />\n1. 將所有認得出樣既鄉黑輯拿歸案<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2k2LOK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2k2LOK.png&h=d3a3673f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左呢張相之外當然仲有其他拍到片清晰見到既人<br />\n最緊要拉打立場姐姐果班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.拉埋何君堯 告佢有份策劃呢場恐襲<br />\n<br />\n3.將李漢文革職查辦 <br />\n要將果晚警察容忍鄉黑殺人付出代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係726星期五晚警鄉黑仲唔作出任何回覆 <br />\n我地將會光復元朗 <br />\n而行動內容我就借隔離巴打公投post一用<br />\n由大家作主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎多次公投！元朗反黑想點搞？純遊行 狗局 鄉議局 鄉黑生意 祠堂！你地揀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1358085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1358085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8cc3c0168bf05577ad22d4469a03762b624d254","tid":1358192,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:20:42.000Z","msg":"大家集思廣益 睇下有冇野要修改 <br />\n例如應該告佢地邊條罪<br />\n小弟文筆唔好 同知識有限<br />\n希望大家幫手一齊諗下或者再組織下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d30bcfc0e200e63f64ec157e98349ef2949dde6","tid":1358192,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:22:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c0558a001afe15d9b6f5afac2ca2e71f3da6f01a","tid":1358192,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:23:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a101c9953c1a77059c8e68be1cede9908cc3e974","tid":1358192,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-